aco）出生於1935年7月6日，2歲時被確認為第十三世達賴喇嘛的轉世靈童。<br />\n<br />\n如今年近80週歲的達賴喇嘛重申之前的態度，明確不會再有靈童轉世。這次接受《倫敦時報》記者採訪時，他說自己可能會轉生成「活潑的金髮碧眼女郎」。如果不巧轉生成了黑人婦女，「那麼她的面孔一定很吸引人。」<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，儘管用轉生為女人調侃話題，達賴喇嘛結束靈童轉世這一在西藏已經延續了600餘年的佛教傳統，實際上是為了擺脫中共當局的控制，因為中共當局早已經明確表示，第十五世達賴喇嘛轉世靈童的認定，必須由中共當局指定，而非按照習俗，由上一世的達賴喇嘛指認。<br />\n<br />\n談起未來，這位諾貝爾和平獎得主表示：「不管未來達賴喇嘛存不存在，佛教將會存在下去。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://ca.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2015/05/18/a1197644.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fca.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2015%2F05%2F18%2Fa1197644.html&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=f467f62e\" target=\"_blank\">http://ca.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2015/05/18/a1197644.html</a><br />\n唔做鬼妹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872c9a1ee690b374b2d779ec117d0c0dd861c1db","tid":1068992,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3d76d66ab200de669cfa66be6f8b2ee0d2be44","tid":1068992,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":40,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"7eb8201fd040212963e19fa653b7c84558b55846","tid":1068992,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"其實轉世系統到或係乜柒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係現世活佛求其篤定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"好似係死左之後第一個bb就係新達賴"},{"pid":"1fd92ee743a5cbfeecf6f3a6e91055f8aba4679c","tid":1068992,"uid":133319,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:14:00.000Z","msg":"UP出黎唔覺得柒架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那狗"},{"pid":"8d9f6e0c661a82745ebba22fbd13fe98bb36f6da","tid":1068992,"uid":78143,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"c